title: EM0156 HelloMarket - Sidebar Store - Main Content Area - Introduction
content:
SuperDeals Extension

Magento SuperDeals extension is a powerful extension that lets you show products have deals on any positions. You can group products by tabs like Today Deals and Weekly Deals

Drag & Drop Page Buider

Our theme is built on EMFramework a Magento theme frameork allows you to layout magento pages endless posibilities with drag & drop UI. No programming required.

Drag & Drop Mega Menu

Build Mega Menu for Magento never easier like this. Unilmited abilities. No code required, You can build your menu like Amazon, Aliexpress, Ebay... effortless

Various Product Widgets

We provide a bunch of product widgets ready to use like Featured, Bestselling, New Products, Filter products in cerntain categories with various sorting order

Excellent Support Team

We have strong team with many years experience in magento development & customization to help you solve any problem quickly

SEO & Code Optimization

Our Magento theme is always optimized for SEO and fast loading. Your store wll get higher rank in search engines. High quality and clean code with detailed user guide.
